Name: Amanda's Sticker Book
About the game: Enjoy a fun match-3 puzzle game for kids and adults alike! Put your matching skills to the test as you swap stickers and use power-ups to clear each puzzle. Amanda is counting on your match-3 talents to make her dreams come true and win the annual sticker book contest and a trip to Hawaii! - 79 levels to complete - More than 20 upgrades - Five rooms to explore - Three useful tools to learn and use - More than a dozen elements to gather
